Author: cliffordsmailman
Text: I kinda relate, like ED and body dismorphia thoughts spark up when I'm around boys, and always shit like "oh you're too ugly for a guy to ever be interested in you" or that I'm too fat or too skinny, but then the too skinny spirals into my thinking that it's not even worth gaining weight because the guys still wouldn't want me because even if I gained a little it probably wouldn't go to the right places and I'm still UGLY and SHORT  so yeah, I do relate ðŸ’€ðŸ’€
